  "detailed_description": "Magic Toenail is a strategic wizarding roguelite where every step you take is a tactical maneuver. You shoot when you move and move when you shoot, so even the simplest enemy encounters can quickly become multi-faceted puzzles!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/23bc6efaf180013bb26a3f7b9f41d660.poster.avif?t=1683046789\" width=500 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/23bc6efaf180013bb26a3f7b9f41d660.webm?t=1683046789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/23bc6efaf180013bb26a3f7b9f41d660.mp4?t=1683046789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WIZARDY WITH PIZAZZ</h2>Each enemy you'll face is made of either Goo, Sparkles, or Whimsy, so you'll have to rearrange your spells each turn to hit these fiends with your desired magical energy ball.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/30369f12f8f1bebcd0f8d8d4c3462e59.poster.avif?t=1683046789\" width=224 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/30369f12f8f1bebcd0f8d8d4c3462e59.webm?t=1683046789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/30369f12f8f1bebcd0f8d8d4c3462e59.mp4?t=1683046789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dozens of hats, cloaks, and eyeballs provide a wealth of varied yet impactful changes to the way your wizard wizzes, but you can only carry one of each at a time, so build your character wisely!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/5b59204475af73c2d4babfdc70943a54.poster.avif?t=1683046789\" width=104 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/5b59204475af73c2d4babfdc70943a54.webm?t=1683046789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/5b59204475af73c2d4babfdc70943a54.mp4?t=1683046789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/3f8b3b707d5ebb4656d6aec59d2a472f.apng?t=1683046789\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/3f8b3b707d5ebb4656d6aec59d2a472f.poster.avif?t=1683046789\" class=\"bb_img\" width=501 height=256 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3+ HOURS OF GAMEPLAY!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>12 bonus challenges!</li><li>Thousands of item combinations!</li><li>Unpredictable synergies and interactions!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Magic Toenail is a strategic wizarding roguelite where every step you take is a tactical maneuver. You shoot when you move and move when you shoot, so even the simplest enemy encounters can quickly become multi-faceted puzzles!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/23bc6efaf180013bb26a3f7b9f41d660.poster.avif?t=1683046789\" width=500 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/23bc6efaf180013bb26a3f7b9f41d660.webm?t=1683046789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/23bc6efaf180013bb26a3f7b9f41d660.mp4?t=1683046789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WIZARDY WITH PIZAZZ</h2>Each enemy you'll face is made of either Goo, Sparkles, or Whimsy, so you'll have to rearrange your spells each turn to hit these fiends with your desired magical energy ball.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/30369f12f8f1bebcd0f8d8d4c3462e59.poster.avif?t=1683046789\" width=224 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/30369f12f8f1bebcd0f8d8d4c3462e59.webm?t=1683046789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393670/extras/30369f12f8f1bebcd0f8d8d4c3462e59.mp4?t=1683046789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dozens of hats, cloaks, and eyeballs provide a wealth of varied yet impactful changes to the way your wizard wizzes, but you can only carry one of each at a time, so build your character wisely!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop play